query: INSERT INTO prices(count, unit_price, receipt_id, product_id) SELECT UNNEST($1::float[]), UNNEST($2::float[]), $3, product_id FROM (SELECT id as product_id FROM products WHERE name IN (SELECT UNNEST($4::text[]))) tmp ON CONFLICT ON CONSTRAINT prices_pkey DO UPDATE SET count=excluded.count, unit_price=excluded.unit_price
